## 6. Per-commit checklist

### Commit 1 — Scripts + tests + CI

- [ ] `git mv` source `scripts/` into `plugins/sulis/scripts/`
- [ ] Move tests subtree
- [ ] Rename CI workflow to `sulis-{{qualifier}}-tests.yml`
- [ ] Edit workflow YAML to point at new paths
- [ ] Edit pass: shebangs, `sys.path.insert`, cache paths, dev fallbacks
- [ ] Verify `find plugins/{{source-plugin}}/scripts -type f` returns empty
- [ ] Commit: `chore(sulis): step 1/5 — move {{source}} scripts + tests + CI into sulis`

### Commit 2 — Skills (with tin-test rename pass)

- [ ] For each skill, `git mv` to new location (with rename per Section 3)
- [ ] For each renamed skill, rewrite `description:` field
- [ ] Update SKILL.md `related_skills:` paths
- [ ] Update internal cross-skill references (`/{{source}}:` → `/sulis:`)
- [ ] Verify `find plugins/{{source-plugin}}/skills -mindepth 1 -type d` returns empty
- [ ] Re-run `detect_collisions.py` → no remaining tin-test failures
- [ ] Commit: `chore(sulis): step 2/5 — move {{N}} {{source}} skills into sulis (with {{M}} tin-test renames)`

### Commit 3 — Agents

- [ ] `git mv` each agent file to `plugins/sulis/agents/`
- [ ] Repo-wide sweep for `subagent_type:` references; edit each cited file
- [ ] Verify `find plugins/{{source-plugin}}/agents -name "*.md"` returns empty
- [ ] Manual smoke test: dispatch the agent once from a Claude session
- [ ] Commit: `chore(sulis): step 3/5 — move {{source}} agents into sulis`

### Commit 4 — References + external ref sweep

- [ ] `git mv` each reference file to `plugins/sulis/references/` (with rename if collision)
- [ ] Apply external ref sweep — work through every category in Section 4
- [ ] Verify `git grep "plugins/{{source-plugin}}/" .` returns no non-historical hits
- [ ] Commit: `chore(sulis): step 4/5 — move {{source}} references into sulis + external ref sweep`

### Commit 5 — Wrap-up

- [ ] Move `docs/` if present (with rename if collision)
- [ ] Mark source plugin `[DEPRECATED]` in: plugin.json, CHANGELOG.md, README.md, CLAUDE.md
- [ ] Bump `plugins/sulis/.claude-plugin/plugin.json` version
- [ ] Add `plugins/sulis/CHANGELOG.md` entry describing the consolidation
- [ ] Bump `.claude-plugin/marketplace.json` sulis version (and marketplace version)
- [ ] Update checkup allowlists if affected
- [ ] Commit: `feat(sulis): v{{new-version}} — {{source}} consolidated into sulis (step 5/5 — wrap-up)`

### Gate 6 — Code-health verification

- [ ] Re-run `/sulis:code-health --raw` → save as `code-health-final.json`
- [ ] Run `compare_baseline.py` → produce `code-health-comparison.md`
- [ ] NEW findings = 0, OR fix-forward in Commit 6 → re-run Gate 6
- [ ] Update `VERIFICATION_REPORT.md` with Gate 6 verdict

